node.text:
Thanks for having me @jesuscalling 🙏🏾
This is a little behind the scenes from my interview, but the full interview will be available on their podcast! 
I had such an awesome time talking about my new book “Feeding the Soul” available 9/28 but you can preorder now! Click link in my bio to order❤️🙏🏾 #tabithabrown #feedingthesoultour #actress #believer #author
Makeup by @brandieonthebeat 
📸 by @4philanthropy

node.title: The world didn’t give you your joy, so don’t let the world take it away❤️

node.text:
Family I am so excited to share this journey with you all! I can’t believe I wrote my first book!! 🙌🏾 OOHHHH GOD I THANK YOU!🙌🏾. I hope y’all enjoy it and I pray it helps someone who may feel stuck in their temporary season!! Thank you all so much for your love and support!! Click the link in my bio or here for the book and tour information: https://linktr.ee/Tabs1choyce
#tabithabrown #believer #wife #mom #author #writer #actress #iwroteabook #thankful #feedingthesoul
Big thank you to @harpercollins and @williammorrowbooks

node.title: Feeding the Soul, because it’s my business! Link in my bio❤️

@harpercollins @williammorrowbooks

node.text:
I know it’s late but I just came across this pic so here goes my Throwback Thursday! 2009
This was the Tab that wasn’t FREE! She was the  constant diet and starving herself for auditions and shoots Tab! Always covering her southern accent Tab!  Always wearing her hair straight, not because she wanted to, but because she thought she had too Tab😔Trying to be what she thought the entertainment industry wanted her to be Tab😔 BUT  then Tab found her way back to the real her 🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾 OOHHHH GOD WE THANK YOU for the journey🙌🏾🙌🏾Now I AM FREE TAB🙌🏾🙌🏾. 
P.S. Donna said to let y’all know she ain’t have nothing to do with the old Tab and that flat iron everyday, but she in control now! 👊🏾
My first book: “Feeding the Soul” is out Sept 28th! I can’t to share more stories about my journey with y’all! Click the link in my bio to order or come hang with me on my book tour! 
Or click here: https://linktr.ee/feedingthesoulbooktour
#tabithabrown #freedom

node.text:
Family I am so excited to share this journey with you all! I can’t believe I wrote my first book!! 🙌🏾 OOHHHH GOD I THANK YOU!🙌🏾. I hope y’all enjoy it and I pray it helps someone who may feel stuck in their temporary season!! Thank you all so much for your love and support!! Click the link in my bio or here for the book and tour information: https://linktr.ee/Tabs1choyce
#tabithabrown #believer #wife #mom #author #writer #actress #iwroteabook #thankful #feedingthesoul
Big thank you to @harpercollins and @williammorrowbooks

node.text: We sure miss cutting up with y’all on “Very Good Mondays” and we are working hard to bring it back soon!! We love blessing small businesses!!! What was your favorite part about VGM?? #tabithabrown #verygoodmondays #choycebrown #supportsmallbusinesses

You are needed and loved in this world I love you! @IAMTABITHABROWN'.

node.text: Today is a huge moment for my family!  My daddy is the first man in his family to make it to 70🙌🏾🙌🏾. OOHHH GOD I THANK YOU!!!! 🙌🏾🙌🏾🙌🏾.
